{"tid":190783,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"得返一個月就考 但好似仲係乜都唔識","createTime":"2017-04-07T10:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T07:51:32.000Z","uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0b9dfee31c3df90fc59c69661f852ce7604f67","tid":190783,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:46:23.000Z","msg":"唔知係我太蠢 定 師傅問題<br />\n依加我連掉頭都未學 泊位又未試過 <br />\n一次都未去過考試個條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n考試有咩要注意 有咩位要做 都唔知<br />\n一星期就得一堂 有時叫佢一星期兩堂 又話無晒位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我係學得慢嘅 俾師傅話過我好蠢 呢樣我自己都知<br />\n其實我係咪可以準備定$510<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b277756fea8d11e18bd71750448d968fa03875","tid":190783,"uid":76336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"臨一個月考先學 學左廿二堂 學密啲 咁就會易入腦啲<br />\n利申 油塘1剔pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2066edd0b3ae6aba4605e0180f5dc7195315680","tid":190783,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"個師傅唔帶你去試場擺明係佢問題啦 唔學唔錯點會識 不過你得返一個月就冇計 祝你一take囉"},{"pid":"0fd7a3a18cd87e71c073b98ce5fe2c925b52d1c8","tid":190783,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個師傅唔帶你去試場擺明係佢問題啦 唔學唔錯點會識 不過你得返一個月就冇計 祝你一take囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0df56476e6216e4a9dd9b4e721bda95d0aff789","tid":190783,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"依加轉c fu係咪嚟唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987acae1e03c5bc8f6460d4c1e100752934441b1","tid":190783,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依加轉c fu係咪嚟唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" c