><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依加轉c fu係咪嚟唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你得返一個月啲師傅多數都唔肯接 你自己youtube睇吓考嗰條線啲片仲好啦 你係考邊度？</blockquote><br />\n澤安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加出緊去學車 好驚又俾cfu屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澤安出名易，一陣學完再上黎講下學成點<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先試左兩次掉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩次都on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就吊唔到極力子 <br />\n一係就吊到 架車慢行 但轉軚唔夠快<br />\n一係就掛住轉軚 夠快 但左腳就鬆左 吊高左極力子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明掉前心入面同自己講 ：我一定要轉軚快+唔好吊過極力子 但一做就on99咁做唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試完兩次想試多次 但已經俾cfu屌撚到聲唔敢出了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23731f6b5b4dd1888940060fe53be254ad52077d","tid":190783,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你學左幾多堂先？棍van？</blockquote><br />\n14堂 係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲係on99咁手腳唔協調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4284fe60e4714290507265ac821bbe7beb5a934","tid":190783,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<br />\n岩岩學完第22.5個鐘<br />\n仲係堂堂俾屌到乜咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點算呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好蠢呀我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時見到街上面啲c9都揸到車 我就諗 我蠢撚到咁不如死左去算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2fd8a8dd90c883f7349cae6990822ef329b115","tid":190783,"uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T16:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係<br />\n岩岩學完第22.5個鐘<br />\n仲係堂堂俾屌到乜咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點算呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好蠢呀我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時見到街上面啲c9都揸到車 我就諗 我蠢撚到咁不如死左去算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n將勤補拙😫😫<br />\n銀彈政策 補多d鐘😫😫<br />\n如果果樣野第一次錯，我會原諒自己<br />\n但如果重複犯罪，就不能接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ac2e8000d192a20d2e9012ed1e01e630434796","tid":190783,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依加轉c fu係咪嚟唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你得返一個月啲師傅多數都唔肯接 你自己youtube睇吓考嗰條線啲片仲好啦 你係考邊度？</blockquote><br />\n澤安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加出緊去學車 好驚又俾cfu屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澤安出名易，一陣學完再上黎講下學成點<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先試左兩次掉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩次都on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就吊唔到極力子 <br />\n一係就吊到 架車慢行 但轉軚唔夠快<br />\n一係就掛住轉軚 夠快 但左腳就鬆左 吊高左極力子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明掉前心入面同自己講 ：我一定要轉軚快+唔好吊過極力子 但一做就on99咁做唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試完兩次想試多次 但已經俾cfu屌撚到聲唔敢出了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似係手腳未協調到 未可以好分得清楚手同腳分別要做啲咩 放心 呢個唔關智商事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 練多幾次就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbce40405a5f1d900a72e8d1dd782fe08b28ba8f","tid":190783,"uid":60840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T22:08:34.000Z","msg":"澤安好易架咋<br />\n大埔道、南昌街都好撚易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我肥撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乙部pass，丙部行到最尾，轉右入返試場個陣回軑太慢，比考官踩撚停左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩之後pass天光道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb457ea6b4e6d19083a22cedbfd588e2b1c42db","tid":190783,"uid":60840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T22:11:12.000Z","msg":"掉頭泊位都係睇marker逐步做架姐<br />\n慢慢掉慢慢泊又唔會扣分，快又唔會加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢做就ok"},{"pid":"e62f945ecf2bd2b61a0480c820cf3873ec27a491","tid":190783,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依加轉c fu係咪嚟唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你得返一個月啲師傅多數都唔肯接 你自己youtube睇吓考嗰條線啲片仲好啦 你係考邊度？</blockquote><br />\n澤安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加出緊去學車 好驚又俾cfu屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澤安出名易，一陣學完再上黎講下學成點<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先試左兩次掉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩次都on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就吊唔到極力子 <br />\n一係就吊到 架車慢行 但轉軚唔夠快<br />\n一係就掛住轉軚 夠快 但左腳就鬆左 吊高左極力子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明掉前心入面同自己講 ：我一定要轉軚快+唔好吊過極力子 但一做就on99咁做唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試完兩次想試多次 但已經俾cfu屌撚到聲唔敢出了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似係手腳未協調到 未可以好分得清楚手同腳分別要做啲咩 放心 呢個唔關智商事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 練多幾次就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係九龍塘學調頭，都學咗6堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慢慢黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左腳hold住磨擦點，車速快慢靠迫力控制。當較岩車速後雙腳定住唔好旭，專注扭呔"},{"pid":"555260abee4950adf9b67467d820a78f604e3252","tid":190783,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係<br />\n岩岩學完第22.5個鐘<br />\n仲係堂堂俾屌到乜咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點算呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好蠢呀我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時見到街上面啲c9都揸到車 我就諗 我蠢撚到咁不如死左去算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地大部分都係揸自動波，竟然用自動波同棍波比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自動波，小學生都識揸啦。我相信宜家俾部九巴你揸，自學返1-2個鐘，分分鐘揸得好過棍van"},{"pid":"8bea45a3f4c0c403bb15e7ebd758ae1655096bad","tid":190783,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:51:32.000Z","msg":"14堂係咪每堂45mins?<br />\n手腳協調既野個個人唔同, 覺得未協調咪操多d, 呢個師傅無堂就搵過第二個<br />\n放膽d 去試, 最多咪死火<br />\n<br />\n其實有少少似踩單車, 你失敗左好多次, 到某個時候就會無啦啦掂左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}